Team is in position.

352
00:30:09,840 --> 00:30:11,353
我们正在前进
We're on the move.

353
00:30:57,080 --> 00:30:59,230
秃鹰 阿尔法到达正厅了
Condor, Alpha's now in the nave.

354
00:30:59,640 --> 00:31:01,995
正在安装设备和遥感系统 完毕
Setting up equipment and telemetry. Over.

355
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:37,592
所以 接下来怎么办
So, what happens now?

356
00:31:40,400 --> 00:31:42,038
他们会来的
